OL,6,FThe family of a British couple who
OL,7,Fhave been detained in Iran have said
OL,8,Ftheir situation is causing
OL,9,F"significant concern".
OL,11,FCraig and Lindsay Foreman were
OL,12,Freportedly detained in January but
OL,13,FIran's state-run media revealed this
OL,14,Fweek they had been accused of security-
OL,15,Frelated offences.
OL,17,FThe couple were ultimately heading for
OL,18,FAustralia, having crossed into Iran
OL,19,Ffrom Armenia on December 30.
