OL,6,FMrs Foreman was reportedly conducting
OL,7,Fa research project during the journey,
OL,8,Fasking people what makes a "good life".
OL,10,FShe had reportedly planned to present
OL,11,Fher findings at a positive psychology
OL,12,Fconference in Brisbane in July.
OL,14,FThe couple had shared a number of
OL,15,Fupdates from Iran and had been
OL,16,Fplanning to enter Pakistan next.
OL,18,F"To put your minds at rest, we are
OL,19,Fhaving the most amazing time in Iran,"
OL,20,Fthey posted on Facebook on January 3.
