OL,6,FBefore embarking on their travel, Mrs
OL,7,FForeman acknowledged on Instagram that
OL,8,Ftravelling to Iran, against the
OL,9,FForeign Office's advice, was "slightly
OL,10,Fscary".
OL,12,F"Yes, we're aware of the risks. But we
OL,13,Falso know the rewards of meeting
OL,14,Fincredible people, hearing their
OL,15,Fstories, and seeing the breathtaking
OL,16,Flandscapes of these regions could far
OL,17,Foutweigh the fear," she said.
