OL,6,F"We are actively engaging with the
OL,7,FBritish government and relevant
OL,8,Fauthorities, working diligently to
OL,9,Fnavigate the complexities of this
OL,10,Fmatter. The family are united in our
OL,11,Fdetermination to secure their safe
OL,12,Freturn."
OL,14,FBritish citizens have previously been
OL,15,Fheld by the Iranian regime.
OL,17,FNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe and Annosheh
OL,18,FAshoori, who are dual British-Iranian
OL,19,Fcitizens, were released in March 2022
OL,20,Fafter being held for several years in
OL,21,FIranian prisons.
